project_address: BLOCK NO. 126, PAIKI SUB DIVISION -B KARADVA, CHORASI

formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
1.Form-2 of Engineer Certificate is upated with Form-3 of CA Certificate till date of BUC date (07.12.2018). The physical visit of Engineer is upto the date of  31.12.2018. There after no data addition in engineer certificate(Form-2).				
2.Amount reported at Sr. No. 7 is the amount withdrawn from designated bank account into which 70% of the amount received from customers towards booking and sale of flats is deposited but excludes all taxes collected from customers.				
				
3.Above figures are certified based on posting in books of accounts as on 31/01/2020. The details in Annexure-A are also as on 31/01/2020.				
				
4.Figures for the period from 01/04/2017 to 31/03/2018 included in above are based on unaudited financial statements and figures for the period from 01/04/2019 to 31/12/2019 included in above are based on provisional unaudited financial statements. 				
				
5.All the flats in respect to which no Agreement of sale hs been exucuted by the promotor. Therefore, in order to avoid error while uploading CA certificate on GujRERA website, date of 1st cheque received against those flats has been mentioned in the column "Date of Agreement for Sale".
